sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User Agent<br/>(Browser)
    participant SPA as SPA Client<br/>(JavaScript App)
    participant Auth as Authorization Server<br/>(e.g., Auth0 / Okta)
    participant API as Resource Server<br/>(Protected API)

    Note over SPA: PKCE Setup Phase
    SPA->>SPA: Generate cryptographic random<br/>code_verifier (43-128 chars)
    SPA->>SPA: Compute code_challenge =<br/>BASE64URL(SHA256(code_verifier))
    SPA->>SPA: Store code_verifier in session storage

    Note over User,Auth: Authorization Phase
    SPA->>User: Redirect to authorization endpoint
    User->>Auth: GET /authorize?<br/>response_type=code<br/>&client_id=spa_client_id<br/>&redirect_uri=https://app.example.com/callback<br/>&scope=openid profile api:read<br/>&state=random_state_value<br/>&code_challenge=E9Melhoa2OwvFrEMTJguCH...<br/>&code_challenge_method=S256

    Auth->>User: Display login form
    User->>Auth: Submit credentials<br/>(username + password)
    Auth->>Auth: Validate user credentials<br/>against identity store

    opt MFA Enabled
        Auth->>User: Request second factor
        User->>Auth: Provide TOTP / push confirmation
        Auth->>Auth: Verify second factor
    end

    Auth->>Auth: Generate authorization_code<br/>Store code_challenge mapping

    Auth->>User: 302 Redirect to callback URL<br/>?code=auth_code_xyz<br/>&state=random_state_value
    User->>SPA: Load callback URL with auth code

    Note over SPA,Auth: Token Exchange Phase
    SPA->>SPA: Validate state parameter<br/>matches stored value
    SPA->>SPA: Retrieve code_verifier<br/>from session storage

    SPA->>Auth: POST /oauth/token<br/>grant_type=authorization_code<br/>&code=auth_code_xyz<br/>&redirect_uri=https://app.example.com/callback<br/>&client_id=spa_client_id<br/>&code_verifier=dBjftJeZ4CVP-mB92K27uhbUJU1p1r_wW1gFWFOEjXk

    Auth->>Auth: Compute SHA256(code_verifier)<br/>and compare with stored code_challenge
    Auth->>Auth: Validate authorization_code<br/>not expired / not reused

    alt PKCE Verification Succeeds
        Auth->>Auth: Generate access_token (JWT)<br/>+ refresh_token + id_token
        Auth->>SPA: 200 OK<br/>{ access_token, refresh_token,<br/>id_token, expires_in: 3600,<br/>token_type: "Bearer" }
    else PKCE Verification Fails
        Auth->>SPA: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{ error: "invalid_grant" }
    end

    Note over SPA,API: Resource Access Phase
    SPA->>SPA: Store tokens securely in memory<br/>(NOT localStorage)

    SPA->>API: GET /api/user/profile<br/>Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJS...
    API->>API: Validate JWT signature<br/>using Auth Server public key
    API->>API: Check token expiration (exp claim)<br/>Verify audience (aud claim)<br/>Verify scopes (scope claim)

    alt Token Valid
        API->>SPA: 200 OK { user profile data }
    else Token Expired
        API->>SPA: 401 Unauthorized<br/>{ error: "token_expired" }
        SPA->>Auth: POST /oauth/token<br/>grant_type=refresh_token<br/>&refresh_token=stored_refresh_token<br/>&client_id=spa_client_id
        Auth->>Auth: Validate refresh token<br/>Check rotation policy
        Auth->>SPA: 200 OK { new access_token,<br/>new refresh_token }
        SPA->>API: Retry request with<br/>new access_token
        API->>SPA: 200 OK { user profile data }
    end

    Note over SPA: Cleanup: Remove code_verifier<br/>from session storage
